# Cloudflare Pages redirects — the /bosc re-root (#307 PR 2).
# The live site (Lima) moved from the root to /bosc so future watershed sites are clean
# siblings (/gcp, …). These keep every old URL — and every corpus citation — working.
# /network/* and the API stay at the root (siblings + serverless), so they are NOT rewritten.

/                       /bosc/                      301
/start                  /bosc/start                 301
/timeline               /bosc/timeline              301
/ask                    /bosc/ask                   301
/submit                 /bosc/submit                301
/about                  /bosc/about                 301
/about-me               /bosc/about-me              301
/site/*                 /bosc/site/:splat           301
/watershed/*            /bosc/watershed/:splat      301
/wiki/*                 /bosc/wiki/:splat           301
/docs/*                 /bosc/docs/:splat           301
/reports/*              /bosc/reports/:splat        301
/walk/*                 /bosc/walk/:splat           301
